  "description": "A long-distance, slightly hazy view of the Golden Gate Bridge spanning a body of water, likely the San Francisco Bay. The bridge is painted a reddish-orange color, standing out against the blue water and muted sky. Alcatraz Island is visible in the distance to the left of the bridge. A small white boat is moving through the water. The sky is a pale, soft gradient from light blue to light peach.  Dark foliage from a tree frames the right side of the image. There are supporting arches visible under the main span of the bridge.",
